<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>cʒwıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_154_line_1577035677178_3396">wıe wır </ab></add> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Eglofſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> dem <expan>Jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd des <expan>gefang<ex>en</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_line_1577035701635_3413">
<del rend="strikethrough">bey vns Jn <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ſchrıft eẅr gnade <expan>ſunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> berürt vnd begert daʒ </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_154_r1l27">
<del rend="strikethrough">der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eglofſt<ex>ein</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_154_r1l25">auf <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> gnaden ſchrıft <expan>ſunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab></add> ʒu <expan>eıne<ex>m</ex></expan> tag gen kıcʒıng 
