<pb facs="#facs_155" id="76v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_155_r1l1"><expan>nehſt<ex>en</ex></expan> ſunntag nach <expan>vınc<ex>u</ex>la<ex>m</ex></expan> Petrȷ ʒu <expan>eıne<ex>m</ex></expan> tag alſo <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_155_r1l2"><expan>ſuche<ex>n</ex></expan> welle So <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> ʒu eren <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_155_r1l3"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> rate auf <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ʒeıt auch darcʒu <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_155_r1l6"><expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dıenſt vnd <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_155_r1l7"><expan>vinc<ex>u</ex>la<ex>m</ex></expan> Petrj </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_154" id="76r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Johanns<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>bisch<ex>of</ex></expan> czu
                                <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> nehst
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, <add>wie wir</add>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>Eglofst<ex>ein</ex></expan> dem <expan>jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add>auf <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> gnaden schrift
                                    <expan>sunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan></add> zu
                                <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> tag gen Kiczing <add>zu</add>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc.,
                        also <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                            <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade
                        <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz uns <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>Eglofst<ex>ein</ex></expan> auf disz zeit
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>umb</expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>
                        hat, daz er auf <app>
<note><q type="date">nu den <pb facs="#facs_155" id="76v"/>
<expan>nehst<ex>en</ex></expan> sunntag nach
                                            <expan>vinc<ex>u</ex>la<ex>m</ex></expan>
                                Petri</q>04.08.1420</note>
</app> zu <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> tag also
                            <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und den <expan>suche<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        welle; so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> zu eren <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> rate
                        auf <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan> zeit auch darczu
                                <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dienst und
                            <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>vinc<ex>u</ex>la<ex>m</ex></expan> Petri.</ab>
</div>
